{"type": "article", "id": 25757, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-21T06:37:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 26490, "name": "Stitx"}, {"id": 26491, "name": "Knit Your Own"}, {"id": 26492, "name": "Splyt Light"}, {"id": 26493, "name": "Get Grubs"}, {"id": 26494, "name": "Phiaro"}, {"id": 24230, "name": "artori design"}, {"id": 16335, "name": "Plumen"}, {"id": 26495, "name": "Wool and the Gang"}, {"id": 26496, "name": "Jason Krugman"}, {"id": 26497, "name": "Scott Leinweber"}, {"id": 26498, "name": "Meroo Seth"}, {"id": 26499, "name": "Nachiket Jadhav"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115059Rg9ZaLkEyXbVroxc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p>\n<h2>Stitx by STITX</h2>\n<p class=\"\">STITX 是一个三人组成的设计团队，成员都是来自新加坡国立大学工业设计专业的学生。以应对快节奏的生活以及越来越紧张的工作空间，他们设计了这个可粘式收纳袋，让你可以轻松地把常用物品放进不同大小的口袋中。除了口袋之外，还有为 13 和 15 寸笔记本电脑设计的收纳袋，就像电脑保护套那样。你可以在他们的<a href=\"http://indiegogo.com/projects/stitx\">众筹页面</a>了解更多信息。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181740eKNkaSt7Im8XJfpy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181741ZmiS3LxIyBrfFzJU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65136719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181741Gp30DU72OvVWKRrz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181742x8atBmbTu0F2XwAM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181743a6M8LyPjlDwH4kGx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181743KiuqWYymkxL8eJM2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67285156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>宠物小空间 by Phiaro</h2>\n<p class=\"\">如果你虽然不希望自己的宠物爬上家具，但同时又想让它们拥有一个自己的空间，<a href=\"http://www.phiaro.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">Phiaro</a> 的设计师们为你想了一个办法：看似普通的茶几下暗藏玄机，让宠物可以在里面小憩，提升了空间的利用率。除此之外，他们还设计了一款穹顶风格的宠物小窝。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181744Aw0gnqaoQFcVDrH1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181744zUae7MHIZgxbNdWO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181745NrfPHyEQXsJdbB4D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.35428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181745EsTozijgh65eNSHB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.35428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181746cO1pRkXlxBC0qhS3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.35428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>supergal bookend + shelf by artori design</h2>\n<p class=\"\">大银幕上的女英雄越来越多了，曾在去年推出过超人书挡的 artori design 很适时地推出了以女超人（supergal）为主题的书挡和书架。斜体的设计配合手中暗藏的磁铁，看上去就好像是女超人飞在半空中“英雄救书”一样。你可以通过链接购买到<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/supergal-bookend-girl-power-keeps-falling-artori-design-03-03-2016/\">书挡</a>和<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/wondershelf-beauty-strength-keep-books-aloft-artori-design-03-03-2016/\">书架</a>。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181746TrAlckYe0wZtoy91.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83618582\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181747HK51Ue9oVQYIP3WD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3190709\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181747Qe1La5mKGsZNIrzn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.03789731\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181748B7znJL6G8d4cybCq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.64902507\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181748R8OMFGgizvdS0nPV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.43765281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Knit Your Own by PLUMEN X Wool and The Gang</h2>\n<p class=\"\">灯具品牌 <a href=\"http://plumen.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Plumen</a> 和 DIY 时尚品牌 <a href=\"http://www.woolandthegang.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Wool and the Gang</a> 携手加入了编结和流苏的回归热潮当中，推出了这个名为 Knit Your Own 的 DIY 羊毛灯罩套装。如果你只是想亲手制作一个羊毛灯罩，在购买时也可以选择不配灯泡。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181749kjF0hXx36OgwWYcI.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071817493vVfR19xeJoSOQML.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181750r7uIGcHloPX0wa1j.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181750X39MdBCEuKs0SwiW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.43\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181751VvfljGsWepZxA3Lk.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.27659574\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Splyt Light by Jason Krugman and Scott Leinweber</h2>\n<p class=\"\">纽约布鲁克林的两位设计师 <a href=\"http://jasonkrugman.com/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://jasonkrugman.com/', 'Jason Krugman');\" target=\"_blank\">Jason Krugman</a> 和 <a href=\"http://scottleinweber.com/\" onclick=\"__gaTracker('send', 'event', 'outbound-article', 'http://scottleinweber.com/', 'Scott Leinweber');\" target=\"_blank\">Scott Leinweber</a> 共同推出了这款名为 Splyt Light 的模块式灯具，它由几种不同造型的配件构成，让你可以自己动手设计出独一无二的“树枝灯”——你只需要搭出想要的造型，再安上灯泡就行了。你可以在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1244118214/splyt-light\">Kickstarter</a> 上看到更多的相关信息。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071817517CoEcKDVJfYOXtxa.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181752FvuCNQGzHVRE91os.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071817522qetLSWz3cEQFTpi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181753t92SZvIV1Bacbp0X.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071817548YG5SVrpIsBb1PvQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Get Grubs by Meroo Seth and Nachiket Jadhav</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这是 Meroo Seth 和 Nachiket Jadhav 为印度的快餐品牌 Get Grubs 所设计的包装。包装采用了温和的色调，上面还拼贴了各种产品和原材料的图案，夹杂在其中的是一系列文字和标语，让这个包装显得更加别具一格。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071817547092qkaSEgYZOVni.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.679\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181755aD6B1VoJ0PMp5yHN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181755DsCpbTNw3E5j9JIl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181756v23t5TPJ4ErRDFIX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607181756S3CirT5zeHQbBWIA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}